Package com.mesosphere.mesos.rx.java.test

This package provides a set of tools to facilitate testing Mesos RxJava clients.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Async.ErrorableRunnable
    Convenience type that allows submitting a runnable that may throw a checked exception.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Async
    A JUnit Rule that provides a convenience method to run async tasks.
    RecordIOUtils
    A set of utilities for dealing with the RecordIO format.
    StringMessageCodec
    MessageCodec for a UTF-8 String
    TcpSocketProxy
    A utility class that can used to create a proxy between Mesos and your client, and then close the connection to verify behavior.
